{"tid":411813,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解班老一輩咁鍾意去飲茶","createTime":"2017-09-24T06:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T10:48:26.000Z","uid":40226,"like":10,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9988d5e603953b8e6f9cc64983040acde80aa706","tid":411813,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母真係on99<br />\n平又唔係平一籠點心廿幾蚊<br />\n又加一又茶費<br />\n嘢食又唔係好食<br />\n稻香嗰啲直頭係大陸工場整<br />\n茶又垃圾<br />\n<br />\n重點係等位耐撚到仆街<br />\n屌你假日食下午茶起碼要等40分鐘<br />\n入到去又要等半個鐘啲嘢食先到<br />\n啲廢老又要喺入面妹下妹下<br />\n食足幾個鐘先走<br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇後生仔鍾意飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係等多幾十年班老嘢死曬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班仆街聽執笠啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308517bd5037ea687bd48c1e81a4e6bbfa59e6b9","tid":411813,"uid":14509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意飲菜食點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間連鎖酒樓啲點心好垃圾"},{"pid":"e4a9a85d19fbe89e399e75b58d89a6c39f0b3224","tid":411813,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"耐唔耐約埋成班朋友飲早茶 大家有講有笑又有野食 有冷氣 張枱又大 不知幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e5289feb0a05b0ece4df0506798dee28093270","tid":411813,"uid":2679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"飲茶好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無同好一星期飲翻次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fd6d9555753d5f73ea836cc33ff4a645676d88","tid":411813,"uid":12201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"成日自己去天橋底茶樓飲 啲野自己做既 又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：後生仔"},{"pid":"c75538624b7407551615d73e15e550bc887f3204","tid":411813,"uid":105149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"茶樓啲炒粉麵又幾好食"},{"pid":"61facfd529dffd2d47e6bf507ecd9699224c3e85","tid":411813,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"個個星期都同屋企人去至少兩次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1b0c9348e71d231e11ce3a68569eab66b12cf2","tid":411813,"uid":72926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"退左休唔洗做 日日好似星期6咁<br />\n大把時間梅下梅下"},{"pid":"5697aa17c1382b90458d4579c8d17a9a185a1bff","tid":411813,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"日本野貴, 飲茶仲貴"},{"pid":"85fe0cac031f1e519972c74a62e45b6f492cdcf8","tid":411813,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶樓啲炒粉麵又幾好食</blockquote><br />\n個啲好有鑊氣"},{"pid":"a6e2fd3040853c3dda11e790d4b27aa9025946ca","tid":411813,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"飲<strong>日日[b]</strong>[b][/"},{"pid":"7f30f94e47641788d2d2d85e6e0d28500f49cb33","tid":411813,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"中學時已經成日同fd lunch time飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ec1cca253044b55b5df81cb6da7199217e1b06","tid":411813,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"人在稻香 一路飲茶一路睇呢個post"},{"pid":"d15271ce2b7b9d1ac31b9370249b10bbc9fdc4ec","tid":411813,"uid":40226,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"仲有晚市就更on9啦<br />\n<br />\n一到大時大節<br />\n屋企啲長輩總係鍾意去酒樓食啲濕鳩套餐<br />\n<br />\n先唔講永遠都係同一menu<br />\n早一兩年稻香非常有新意地推出一個乜春十大簋<br />\n十碟有三碟係烚菜<br />\n屌你老母收成千幾二千<br />\n之前仲有個朋友話好正常<br />\n屌你食屎大呀<br />\n我承認好食嘅中菜可以好貴<br />\n但唔係呢啲垃圾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話多人唔知食乜好<br />\n<br />\n咁去大排檔囉<br />\n平過佢又好食過佢<br />\n<br />\n你話大排檔環境差<br />\n我唔認為酒樓好好囉<br />\n屌你地下啲地墊洗又洗唔到<br />\n啲廢老又成鳩日隨地吐痰<br />\n成個場又嘈到仆街<br />\n點解？<br />\n因為我地要自己洗碗囉<br />\n梗係嘈啦<br />\n出去食都要洗碗on撚9<br />\n<br />\n你話你可以唔洗架<br />\n收皮啦啲碗仲有積架<br />\n點撚樣唔洗呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貼錢買難受</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f27635f528c8cc665dbb39375dfc98db29d98a","tid":411813,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有晚市就更on9啦<br />\n<br />\n一到大時大節<br />\n屋企啲長輩總係鍾意去酒樓食啲濕鳩套餐<br />\n<br />\n先唔講永遠都係同一menu<br />\n早一兩年稻香非常有新意地推出一個乜春十大簋<br />\n十碟有三碟係烚菜<br />\n屌你老母收成千幾二千<br />\n之前仲有個朋友話好正常<br />\n屌你食屎大呀<br />\n我承認好食嘅中菜可以好貴<br />\n但唔係呢啲垃圾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話多人唔知食乜好<br />\n<br />\n咁去大排檔囉<br />\n平過佢又好食過佢<br />\n<br />\n你話大排檔環境差<br />\n我唔認為酒樓好好囉<br />\n屌你地下啲地墊洗又洗唔到<br />\n啲廢老又成鳩日隨地吐痰<br />\n成個場又嘈到仆街<br />\n點解？<br />\n因為我地要自己洗碗囉<br />\n梗係嘈啦<br />\n出去食都要洗碗on撚9<br />\n<br />\n你話你可以唔洗架<br />\n收皮啦啲碗仲有積架<br />\n點撚樣唔洗呀